Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.83,0:00:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This could be your last chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.64,0:00:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember this fondly!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.21,0:00:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap, I'm gonna die...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.29,0:00:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I have anything left...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.08,0:00:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,...I can fire at her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.04,0:00:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Why am I dreaming about that now?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.25,0:00:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The Empress!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.04,0:02:30.92,Ep Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(950,900)\blur1.5\pos(1005.3,889.2)\}Episode 9
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.04,0:02:30.92,Ep Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(950,900)\blur1.5\pos(1500.9,889.2)\fscx80}The Day Love Died
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.25,0:02:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This feels so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.84,0:02:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.25,0:02:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry, I just felt like someone was\Nbehind me in the shower.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.75,0:02:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh god, that's like, so like a horror movie!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.88,0:02:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.38,0:02:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.54,0:02:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a monster in the bathroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.38,0:03:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,There's all kinds of creepy monsters in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.46,0:03:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially when you're all in there naked.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.17,0:03:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what I mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.08,0:03:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,God, stop being ridiculous and come help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.67,0:03:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a monster that was just\Na woman's head with long hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.46,0:03:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a head...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.21,0:03:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.29,0:03:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It wouldn't be able to soak in the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.42,0:03:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,God!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.38,0:03:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you please take us seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.92,0:03:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.38,0:03:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Just woke up on the wrong side of the bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.58,0:03:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm gonna go back to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.29,0:03:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Nomura!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.34,0:03:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out right this second!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.50,0:03:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, it doesn't look like\Nyou're getting back to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.96,0:03:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.00,0:03:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.71,0:03:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.00,0:03:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.00,0:03:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.21,0:03:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Get it together, alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.79,0:03:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha-?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.67,0:03:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-you've got stamps!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.50,0:03:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And you only need one more?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.21,0:03:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Nomura!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.96,0:03:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah! Don't freak out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.25,0:04:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.79,0:04:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He's incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.29,0:04:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate he'll get all the stamps.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.42,0:04:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.79,0:04:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.88,0:04:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The last one he needs is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.17,0:04:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The Empress has left her room.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.42,0:04:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Since a few days ago, she has drastically increased\Nthe amount of carbohydrates in her diet...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.46,0:04:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,...what is called carb-loading, if you will,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.50,0:04:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and now that she is prepared, she is on the move.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.71,0:04:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you are informed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.54,0:04:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.17,0:04:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Message to staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.29,0:04:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No classes today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.25,0:05:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You're late!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.58,0:05:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, mornings ain't easy on guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.40,0:05:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Kikakujo?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.17,0:05:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,She's busy at the girls' dorm this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.54,0:05:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.21,0:05:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently some things have gone missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.17,0:05:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,U. Baragasaki was making a fuss,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.42,0:05:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and I hear Hanasaka's little bear\Nhas gone missing, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.96,0:05:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Do-mo's missing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.63,0:05:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I think he's just off playing somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.54,0:05:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.46,0:05:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Do-mo! Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.63,0:05:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.83,0:05:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.33,0:05:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No sign of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.96,0:05:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Our search did not bear fruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.08,0:05:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Could he have gone towards the school building?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.54,0:05:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not want to make a big deal out of this...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.63,0:05:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.88,0:05:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Satori.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.75,0:06:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If that girl found Do-mo somewhere out of sight,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.10,0:06:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,she would treat him like a stuffed animal\Nand be much too rough with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.08,0:06:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,O-oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.96,0:06:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,N-no...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.75,0:06:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Expand our search to the school!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.88,0:06:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We must find him before\NPrincess Satori does, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.42,0:06:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.17,0:06:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You two!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.88,0:06:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Kikakujo?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.13,0:06:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If you could, could you please\Nhelp me with my search?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.00,0:06:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, search for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.21,0:06:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,A wig!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.50,0:06:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.46,0:06:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.29,0:06:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,A wig?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.50,0:06:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Chouka's "Cho-kyute!" blonde hair\Nis nowhere to be found!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.46,0:06:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.21,0:06:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.33,0:06:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,She hasn't been able to go\Nanywhere this morning because of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.04,0:07:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Chouka, you're so exceedingly pitiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.21,0:07:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got to find it as soon as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.92,0:07:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, so she...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.50,0:07:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,...was wearing a wig.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.86,0:07:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you as soon as we find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.28,0:07:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What "problem" should I pop my head into?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.79,0:07:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I was looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.25,0:07:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Mi...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.21,0:07:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, S-Satori.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.71,0:07:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.21,0:07:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,'Cause I'm Satori now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.21,0:07:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone seems busy today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.50,0:07:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Inaba!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.54,0:07:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,U-umm, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.88,0:07:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this about the wig?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.33,0:07:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Nono...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.33,0:07:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, I don't know about it, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.38,0:07:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You knew it was missing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.83,0:07:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I heard the commotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.71,0:07:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Where on Earth did it go...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.88,0:08:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall I come with...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.04,0:08:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,How disappointing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.83,0:08:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.83,0:08:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.25,0:08:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That little bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.29,0:08:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Warabi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.75,0:08:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We haven't seen hide nor hair...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.85,0:08:19.52,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\bord\blur4.5\pos(1351.999,661)\b0}Hide nor hair
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.54,0:08:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, the hair was hidden!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.77,0:08:24.48,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\bord4.5\blur4.5\pos(456,645)}Hide the hair
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.48,0:08:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We've searched everywhere it could possibly be!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.13,0:08:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We may find it somewhere unexpected...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.84,0:08:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, it's been slipping off a bit recently...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.50,0:08:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it really slipping off that much?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.17,0:08:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's no use asking people...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.08,0:08:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.75,0:08:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The walls are nary without ears, nor eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.04,0:08:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The walls are Mary?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.25,0:08:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, if they find out we've lost it,\Nthey could blame us for being irresponsible!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.04,0:08:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Fret not.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.63,0:08:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I will own the whole ordeal!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.67,0:08:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.63,0:08:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.04,0:09:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is Hanasaka going to own the wig?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.13,0:09:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, d'ya find it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.42,0:09:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.38,0:09:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Kikakujo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.83,0:09:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.96,0:09:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Nomura!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.42,0:09:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,How's it going over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.58,0:09:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.13,0:09:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I-in any case, merci, Miss Warabi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.54,0:09:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you thanking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.25,0:09:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hurry and find it so you\Nwon't have to own it, Miss Warabi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.38,0:09:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.92,0:09:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But why are you going this far, Princess Kikaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.42,0:09:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.25,0:09:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all for that cute girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.88,0:09:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,R-right, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.75,0:09:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go at it again with vigor!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.38,0:09:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.25,0:09:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,For Kyo-bo!\NFor Chouka!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.82,0:09:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyo-bo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.13,0:09:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, guys, you're looking for different things.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.92,0:09:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,She's looking for a cub, and she's looking for a wig.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.96,0:09:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,A cub?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.25,0:09:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,A wig!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.67,0:09:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget that, we've got to find Do-mo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.71,0:09:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make light of it like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.33,0:09:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Do-mo is a living being!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.54,0:10:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Chouka can't live without that wig!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.42,0:10:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't convince me with that\Nhair-splitting argument!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.00,0:10:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, you two, why don't you just look for it toge...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.50,0:10:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Together...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.94,0:10:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a monster that was just\Na woman's head with long hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.88,0:10:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I've solved the case, Watson.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.79,0:10:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Feels so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.67,0:10:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Masuko was so right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.63,0:10:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That monster must've been\Na figment of our imagination!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.29,0:10:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry I scared you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.38,0:10:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's totally fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.33,0:10:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Not again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.02,0:10:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.92,0:10:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.75,0:10:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't come in when us ladies are showering!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.83,0:10:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.79,0:10:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.75,0:10:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.42,0:11:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Bingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.79,0:11:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So you unmasked the monster\Nin the boys' bathroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.04,0:11:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Onee-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.21,0:11:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Nono...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.38,0:11:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.63,0:11:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ubaraga--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.46,0:11:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The regina delle farfalle!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.40,0:11:24.41,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\bord4.5\blur4.5\fs54\pos(944.001,63)}Queen of the Butterflies
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.41,0:11:24.41,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\blord3\blur4.5\fscy90\pos(958.001,613)}Chouka
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.41,0:11:24.41,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\bord4.5\blur4.5\pos(984,1083)}Baragasaki
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.38,0:11:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Just call me Ubaragasaki today...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.46,0:11:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So she's the regina delle farfalle?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.63,0:11:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, she's regina delle--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.83,0:11:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You can simply call me Ubaragasaki today!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.67,0:11:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.67,0:11:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget that, did you find my wig?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.96,0:11:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.30,0:11:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy was havin' a bit of fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.46,0:11:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor Chouka!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.29,0:11:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! We don't have any time to be getting down!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.50,0:11:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't hurry and get ready, we'll be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.75,0:12:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Onee-sama, haven't you heard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.38,0:12:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Heard what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.72,0:12:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Class is canceled today!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.71,0:12:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.96,0:12:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.38,0:12:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,the Empress has gone missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.50,0:12:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.50,0:12:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Amou?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.92,0:12:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Amou?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.25,0:12:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Her striking hand was less like a chop, more like...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.88,0:12:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,...a blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.33,0:12:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But "empress" means she's a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.88,0:12:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she really that Amou?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.94,0:12:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad he was found before\NPrincess Satori found him,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.38,0:12:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,but her lack of movement is actually quite unsettling.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.79,0:12:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of Satori, Princess...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.83,0:13:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,About Misogi...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.30,0:13:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.92,0:13:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.83,0:13:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.17,0:13:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,B-but, i-if we don't do something...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.04,0:13:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you to calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.30,0:13:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Satori doesn't have time for that right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.71,0:13:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.83,0:13:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I would rather be feared than loved,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.25,0:13:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,if I had to choose one...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.17,0:13:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But Tamaba Satori,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.67,0:13:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,you're a monster who possesses both.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.08,0:13:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I get that a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.08,0:13:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Your lonesome self finds a place\Nwhere you can look down on others,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.60,0:14:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,then you dye all those around you in your own colors.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.33,0:14:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only one copy of that photo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.75,0:14:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,How did she...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.68,0:14:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Though I can't support your methods,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.54,0:14:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I can say that it's quite interesting\Nhow they've granted you control.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.33,0:14:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,However, you've developed the need\Nto constantly create new enemies,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.08,0:14:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,then take them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.08,0:14:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But you've provoked the wrong person.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.18,0:14:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Tamaba Satori.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.63,0:14:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You pitiful soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.58,0:14:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You have nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.46,0:14:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No ideals, no ideas, no reasons;\Nyou've lost sight of everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.33,0:14:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,simply wandering towards your next enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.29,0:14:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.13,0:14:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.42,0:14:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What would Nomura say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.92,0:14:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna see Nomura.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.00,0:15:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Satori and Misogi's relationship\Ncertainly seems unnatural...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.63,0:15:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,My goodness, the more I learn,\Nthe more complicated it becomes...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.84,0:15:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,There was one more thing I learned just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.29,0:15:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The Empress left her room?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.08,0:15:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I really don't want there to be any more trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.67,0:15:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,There's already trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.33,0:15:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-that's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.50,0:15:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyo-bo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.75,0:15:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll come with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.17,0:15:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.17,0:15:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.75,0:15:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.17,0:15:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,can I go now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.83,0:15:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,N-no!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.13,0:15:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I-it's a trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.72,0:15:59.43,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\bord4.5\blur4.5\pos(979.999,731.001)}Keishi School: Quick-Draw
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.73,0:16:02.69,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(877.999,575)\blur4.5\bord4.5}Matchless Return
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.96,0:16:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,A single strike, your intentions concealed...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.63,0:16:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.83,0:16:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't sense it coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.03,0:16:21.00,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(940.001,637)\bord4.5\blur4.5}Auto-counter
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.29,0:16:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But it doesn't matter to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.33,0:16:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Satori!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.71,0:16:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You are a pitiful soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.88,0:16:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But I cannot forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.46,0:16:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You have nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.58,0:16:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I will take everything you've built until now
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.04,0:16:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and destroy it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.13,0:16:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I-it didn't hit, why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.75,0:16:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Blow darts are such curious things!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.25,0:16:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.38,0:16:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Who're you looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.71,0:17:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Move, move, out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.21,0:17:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep your friends close, and your enemies closer...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.96,0:17:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd kept her within arm's reach\Nto keep a close watch on her,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.67,0:17:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,but I cannot believe she's tried to steal a march on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.71,0:17:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It is times like these when I wish I had you, Nomura!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.71,0:17:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Misogi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.54,0:17:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.29,0:17:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This taste...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.21,0:17:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You're sisters?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.13,0:17:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I liked high-up places.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.58,0:17:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I liked looking down on people from high-up places.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.50,0:18:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That was where I belonged.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.58,0:18:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It was my spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.63,0:18:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But she...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.75,0:18:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,she stole everything from me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.13,0:18:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Satori's up top!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.50,0:18:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Misogi's on bottom!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.71,0:18:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.42,0:18:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the first time I knew how I looked\Nwhen I looked down on my little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.08,0:18:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Since then, she acted like she was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.54,0:18:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Even our mother thought my little sister was Satori.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.82,0:18:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything she has, she's stolen from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.54,0:18:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,My face, my name, my future...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.79,0:18:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet, I still...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.83,0:19:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.13,0:19:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, jeez!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.21,0:19:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how to react when you say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.17,0:19:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-what?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.92,0:19:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you don't need to despair anymore, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.86,0:19:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I was too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.34,0:19:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I see you're in the middle of something;\Nperhaps I should come again?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.21,0:19:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What? I'm just finishing up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.67,0:19:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And now I don't have to go find you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.17,0:19:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,These things are best when wrapped up all at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.50,0:19:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.83,0:20:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to leave this place!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.04,0:20:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.86,0:20:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You've made quite the mess so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.96,0:20:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be prepared to lose\Nat least an arm for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.86,0:20:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course, it will be two on one!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.35,0:20:13.81,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\bord4.5\blur4.5\pos(982.001,770.501)\b1}Bear Swordsmanship
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.27,0:20:18.61,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\bord4.5\blur4.5\b1\pos(937.999,789)}Switch
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.98,0:20:20.69,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(982.001,619)\bord4.5\blur4.5}Woman and Beast as One
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.28,0:20:24.28,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\bord4.5\blur4.5\b1\pos(954,719)}Simultaneous Slice
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.66,0:20:28.66,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(997.999,701)\bord\blur4.5}Auto-Counter: Tiger's Claw
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.66,0:20:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What is her body made of?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.71,0:20:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,My sword and her claws didn't cut her!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.79,0:20:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Like she's made of steel!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.88,0:20:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Bear blood stinks too much to bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.96,0:20:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Warabi Hanasaka, you are an arrogant soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.36,0:20:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you really think you could do\Nanything to me with your weak body?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.96,0:20:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Your insolence knows no bounds!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.46,0:20:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So much happened today, but this should mean\Neverything's wrapped up, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.42,0:21:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.67,0:21:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.83,0:21:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.63,0:21:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You've been real quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.88,0:21:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-what?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.46,0:21:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl with the sword,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.67,0:21:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,is that kid one of the Five Swords, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.92,0:21:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Inaba Tsukuyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.38,0:21:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The Academy's strongest pigtailed girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.54,0:21:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The only middle-school student in the five Swords!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.13,0:21:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a cool beauty that guys, girls,\Nand even the Five Swords are terrified of!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.75,0:21:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.79,0:21:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna get my last stamp.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.54,0:21:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.67,0:21:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.21,0:21:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,She's super dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.29,0:21:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.88,0:21:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Too late anyhow.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.79,0:23:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Omugi here!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.46,0:23:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiko here!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.04,0:23:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Amou, the Empress, has finally gone on the move!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.92,0:23:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,She seems really used to the field of battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.00,0:23:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,She intentionally making an escape route\Nto catch her opponent off-guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.46,0:23:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And even when someone tries to corner her,\Nshe comes back with intent!
Dialogue: 1,0:23:36.96,0:23:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,With all that, she's totally got it easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.58,0:23:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Intent that won't be deceived by intent!
